name: Release: 1.13.4-015
body:
Changes since last release:

- Removed some retail-only buttons
- Various localisation fixes
- Datastore_crafts: changed the way RecipeIDs are stored
- Workarounds to handle secondary profession recipe books and the two molten core enchanting recipes (which have too many spaces in their names)
- Bugfix for search box being case sensitive

name: Release: 1.13.4-013
body:
Fixes for Duplicate gathering professions
TOC update for WoW Classic patch 1.13.4
Account sharing: checking an item should now check the character it is an item of

name: Alpha: Update for WoW patch 1.13.4
body: No actual addon changes in this version, just patching the version number for WoW patch 1.13.4. Make a ticket in the Issue Tracker if you find any issues.

name: Altoholic Classic v012
body:
- Fixes for profession tracking
- Reduced number of Grids columns to 10
- Fixes for account sharing
- ItemButton code fixes

name: Altoholic Classic v011
body:
- Removed Grids_Dailies and Grids_Dungeons
- Fixes to track gathering professions
- Fixes to track crafting professions when their crafting profession window is opened
- Fix to not track Beast Training as a profession
- Fixes to Account Sharing, though it is not completely working yet, and I am unable to fix this myself as I don't have two accounts.

name: Teelo's Altoholic Classic Fork
body: Fixes for tracking Fishing skill.

name: Teelo's Altoholic Classic Fork
body: Migrated in roughly 70% of the changes Thaoky made with his Altoholic Classic release. This version should be much more stable. Along the same thing Thaoky said: No Agenda/Spells/Talents support. Those folders should be deleted completely.

name: Teelo's Altoholic Classic Fork
body: Fixed a tooltip LUA error caused by unfixed void storage code.

name: Teelo's Altoholic Classic Fork
body: Removal of various redundant expansion code, such as achievements, archaeology, garrisons, void storage, etc. Thanks to https://github.com/davidcraig for this work.

name: Teelo's Altoholic Classic Fork
body: More bugfixes for profession tracking.

name: Teelo's Altoholic Classic Fork
body: Implemented fixes by Kryd0s to get Account Sharing working.

name: Teelo's Altoholic Classic Fork
body: Removed a Garrison reference and fixed a couple LUA errors.

name: Teelo's Altoholic Classic Fork
body: Replaced broken Icon references with ones that exist in Classic.

name: Teelo's Altoholic Classic Fork
body: Fixes to recipe tracking.

name: First release of Teelo's Altoholic Classic Fork
body: Inventory management seems to be working. I've made a start on Tradeskills but it needs work. Enchanting isn't working properly. Quests needs work.
